(1)Click on 5th icon (Extensions)>> search "Live Sass Compiler" >>install it (If not installed)

(2)Create html file than create scss file >> after creating scss file, click on "Watch Sass" 
on footer portion, it will generate css file automatically, than attach this css file in our html file.

(3)To run file we need to install "Live Server"(If not installed) by using 5th icon (Extensions)
(4)We will include css file in our html file and we will work on scss file.
(5)To create separate file for mixin and varialbe, we use _ character(this is mandatory),
   with .scss extension.
   
   
   
   